  ${
    $d x ps $.  $d y ph $.  $d x ch $.  $d x A $.  $d x y $.
    tfis3.1 $e |- ( x = y -> ( ph <-> ps ) ) $.
    tfis3.2 $e |- ( x = A -> ( ph <-> ch ) ) $.
    tfis3.3 $e |- ( x e. On -> ( A. y e. x ps -> ph ) ) $.
    $( Transfinite Induction Schema with implicit substitution. $)
    tfis3 $p |- ( A e. On -> ch ) $=
